description: This is a basic quiz of the Walking Dead: TV Show on AMC. It contains 15 questions and will use only 5 each round you play. You will answer the question by using the number given before the answer option. This is a fan-made alexa skill. All the credit of The Walking Dead goes toward AMC and Robert Kirkman.
